window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Here are some of the finest fairytales from around the world - most of them old favorites: \"Sleeping Beauty,\" \"Rumpelstiltskin,\" \"Cinderella,\" three from \"The Arabian Nights,\" and many more. Andrew Lang was one of the most famous literary critics around 1900. He also edited a series of children's fable books that preserved and illustrated a host of tales which are still used extensively today.</p>"; 
